node.text:
Next Wednesday I am sending out a #JayMail, breaking down exactly what training split you should be following, to remove any of the confusion for you. 

This will be based on your personal needs. 

I will show you step by step how to select the right training split for you. 

Some people should be on a 4 day split, others should be on a 5 or 6 day split 

Next Wednesday I explain exactly how to decide which one is best for you on #JayMail...

You don’t want to miss this! 

Click the JAYMAIL tab in my Linktree in bio to join JayMail for FREE!

node.title: Is your training split holding you back!!?

node.text:
I have been writing #JayMail for over 2 years now, which is a FREE daily email I send you loaded with tips on building size and burning fat. 

With #JayMail I give you:

✅ FREE workouts

✅ Training methods to speed up progress

✅ Dieting advice to help you avoid frustration and months of wasted time eating the wrong things 

My #JayMail readers will tell you this content is super helpful!

I am gonna set up a Gainz Only leg program this week to
help everyone SHOCK  the legs to GROW

You can join for FREE by clicking my link in the bio!

https://jaymail.jaycutler.club

node.text:
In the beginning, I never imagined actually being a MR Olympia. There were only 8 winners ever in the contest history, the most famous of course Arnold with 7 victories. 
I would comb the magazines I found laying around the gym for routines, tips to improve, and the many “secrets” I thought existed to be a bodybuilder. In fact, I never had seen a pro in person, only in books. 
I had read probably the most influential book at a young age that I purchased at a local GNC. This books title was Beyond Built by a fella named Bob Paris. 
Bob in my opinion had one of the most impressive and balanced physiques I’ve ever witnessed. That book taught me a lot, in fact I used to to build much of my knowledge in the beginning. 
The journey. I’m sitting here thinking of all the time I buried myself in books and learning routines of the pros..... I spent hours in the gym training, but also I observed from a distance how to workout around my peers. 
  Today we have it easier. You want to learn, you turn on YouTube, IG .. search your favorite influencer, type in the routine you want and bingo.... it’s just that easy.  Here is a short story of how I battled the Olympia... I was 15th to 8th to many 2nd places, till I became the best... 2 years in a row.... lost the title and became the first and only one in history to win that title back. I became a 4 time winner of the Mr Olympia. 

Ask me on Aug 3, 1991 if that would ever happen??. My story is a real one , and for all those people that were there since the beginning ....this one is especially for you.  JC

I’m due for a trip back to Sterling MA 🔜 
Proud of my roots. I spent many weekends early on, doing push ups in my room … staying with my Mom and my Stepdad Paul’s home on the Army base, Fort Devens 

My early photos hitting bicep poses in my Moms kitchen and telling her “Someday Mom, I’m gonna be on a bodybuilding stage.” 
My Mom never missed one contest!! 🙏❤️

**Do you want to make your arms grow over the next 6 weeks?** 

Next week on #JayMail I am sending out a 6 week training guide for arms.

I want to see how much size you can add in 6 weeks, using this arm guide I am giving away. 

If you do everything I outline you will see a big difference 💪🏻! 

The best part is that this is 100% FREE to access.
